<br>
For example, the plot is basically there is this big end of the world kind of war and the aftermath. From there you could decide one character will be a soldier, one could be a politician, the other could be a civilian...things like that.<br>
<br>
Now, for creating characters first...This is real simple. Basically just make up characters with interesting personalities. You won't be able to give them to much of past, but what information you will be able to give can help form your plot. For instance, say you have a brother and sister. They don't have their parents and the sister is very strange(special powers, diffrent species,ect)that sets her appart drastically either from her brother or everyone else. (Most likely everyone else because if the two were related they would share similar qualities) Now for the plot, because this girl is so special, some people(Scientists, government, mafia,whatever)decide they want her. So, basically the two end up running and getting into trouble.<br>
<br>
